Package org.certificateservices.custom.c2x.ieee1609dot2.generator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthorityCertGenerator
    Certificate Generator class for generating certificates of types: RootCA, Short Term CA (App) and Long Term CA (Enroll).
    AuthorizationCertGenerator
    Certificate Generator class for Authorization Cert, used by a Short Term (App) CA, using end entity certificate with certificateRequest permissions.
    BaseAuthorityCertGenerator
    Certificate Generator class for generating certificates of types: RootCA, Short Term CA (App) and Long Term CA (Enroll).
    BaseCertGenerator
    Base CertGenerator class containing common methods.
    CertChainBuilder
    Class containing methods to build a certificate chain from a set of known certificates and a trust store of root certificates.
    DecryptAndVerifyResult
    Value Object class representing result of a SecuredDataGenerator.decryptAndVerifySignedData operation.
    DecryptResult
    Value Object class representing result of a SecuredDataGenerator.decrypt operation.
    EncryptResult
    Value Object class representing result of a SecuredDataGenerator.encrypt operation.
    EnrollmentCertGenerator
    Certificate Generator class for Enrollment Cert, used by a Long Term CA, using end entity certificate with certificateRequest permissions.
    ImplicitCertificateData
    Special case of generated structure containing a implicit certificate along with the r value used to construct the related private key.
    SecuredCrlGenerator
    Base SecuredCRLGenerator class containing classes to generated signed CRL files
    SecuredDataGenerator
    Base CertGenerator class containing common methods.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SecuredDataGenerator.SignerIdentifierType
    Class indicating what kind for signer identifier that should be included in a signed secure data.
